#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-22-quarkus-newsletter-67.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Curated online stories, articles, and videos about Quarkus are available in the April 2026 edition of the Quarkus Newsletter."
msgstr "2026 年 4 月版《夸克通讯》提供了有关夸克的在线故事、文章和视频。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-04-22-quarkus-newsletter-67.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Read \"Build a Streaming AI Chat in Java with Quarkus, Vaadin, and LangChain4j\", a hands-on guest post by Sebastian Kühnau showing how to stream LLM responses token by token in a pure Java UI with Vaadin Flow and Quarkus. Check out Mario Fusco's post to learn our reasoning behind enabling by default in the Quarkus 3.35 release. Scivics Lab wrote a post \"quarkus-chat-ui: A Web Front-End for LLMs, and a Real-World Case for POJO-actor\" that introduces a new Chat UI component built with Vaadin and designed to integrate seamlessly into a Quarkus application, simplifying the creation of conversational interfaces. They then follow with another \"quarkus-chat-ui (2): The Actor Design Behind LLM-to-LLM Conversation\" so you can see how to actually use POJO-actor in quarkus-chat-ui, a Quarkus-based LLM chat UI that connects to Claude Code CLI, vLLM, and other backends. Learn how to integrate Redis caching and data storage in a Quarkus Java application using the Quarkus Redis extension with reactive by reading \"How to Use Redis with Quarkus in Java\" by Nawaz Dhandala. Markus Eisele wrote \"AI Coding Tools in 2026: How to Work With Agents Without Losing Control\" a Java engineer’s operating model: Ask/Plan/Code flows, guardrails, and review discipline at scale."
msgstr "阅读 \"使用 Quarkus、Vaadin 和 LangChain4j 在 Java 中构建流式 AI 聊天\"，这是一篇由 Sebastian Kühnau 撰写的实践客座文章，展示了如何使用 Vaadin Flow 和 Quarkus 在纯 Java UI 中逐个令牌流式传输 LLM 响应。查看 Mario Fusco 的文章，了解我们在 Quarkus 3.35 版本中默认启用 LLM 的原因。Scivics 实验室撰写了一篇题为 \"quarkus-chat-ui：这篇文章介绍了使用 Vaadin 构建的新聊天 UI 组件，该组件旨在无缝集成到 Quarkus 应用程序中，从而简化对话界面的创建。随后，他们还介绍了另一个 \"quarkus-chat-ui (2)\"：LLM-to-LLM对话背后的代理设计\"，这样你就可以看到如何在quarkus-chat-ui中实际使用POJO-actor，这是一个基于Quarkus的LLM聊天用户界面，可以连接到Claude Code CLI、vLLM和其他后端。阅读纳瓦兹-丹达拉（Nawaz Dhandala）撰写的《如何在 Java 中使用 Redis 与 Quarkus》（How to Use Redis with Quarkus in Java）一文，了解如何在 Quarkus Java 应用程序中使用 Quarkus Redis 扩展与 reactive 集成 Redis 缓存和数据存储。Markus Eisele 撰写的《2026 年的人工智能编码工具：如何在不失去控制的情况下与代理合作》是 Java 工程师的操作模式：大规模的询问/计划/编码流程、护栏和审查纪律。"

